t trade-off between\ncommunication complexity and control cost.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2012 12:53:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Feb 2012 16:32:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-02-02"}
